<node TEXT="Posted" ID="ID_1510151575" CREATED="1406792676871" MODIFIED="1406792756232">
<node TEXT="on Aug 16, 2013 by Jeff Knupp" ID="ID_1853230928" CREATED="1406792758302" MODIFIED="1406792758302"/>
<node TEXT="http://www.jeffknupp.com/blog/2013/08/16/open-sourcing-a-python-project-the-right-way/" ID="ID_1204121696" CREATED="1406792639534" MODIFIED="1406792639534" LINK="http://www.jeffknupp.com/blog/2013/08/16/open-sourcing-a-python-project-the-right-way/"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="Most Python developers have written at least one tool, script, library" ID="ID_827281359" CREATED="1406792949835" MODIFIED="1406792949835">
<node TEXT="or framework that others would find useful. My goal in this article is" ID="ID_1959559465" CREATED="1406792949835" MODIFIED="1406792949835"/>
<node TEXT="to make the process of open-sourcing existing Python code as clear and" ID="ID_1214111045" CREATED="1406792949851" MODIFIED="1406792949851"/>
<node TEXT="painless as possible. And I don&apos;t simply mean, &quot;create GitHub repo," ID="ID_772953288" CREATED="1406792949851" MODIFIED="1406792949851"/>
<node TEXT="git push, post on Reddit, and call it a day.&quot; By the end of this" ID="ID_1852193841" CREATED="1406792949852" MODIFIED="1406792949852"/>
<node TEXT="article, you&apos;ll be able to take an existing code base and transform it" ID="ID_17879970" CREATED="1406792949852" MODIFIED="1406792949852"/>
<node TEXT="into an open source project that encourages both use and contribution." ID="ID_807109561" CREATED="1406792949853" MODIFIED="1406792949853"/>
<node TEXT="While every project is different, there are some parts of the process" ID="ID_761403843" CREATED="1406792949853" MODIFIED="1406792949853"/>
<node TEXT="of open-sourcing existing code that are common to all Python" ID="ID_926210389" CREATED="1406792949854" MODIFIED="1406792949854"/>
<node TEXT="projects. In the vein of another popular series I&apos;ve written," ID="ID_1034773572" CREATED="1406792949855" MODIFIED="1406792949855"/>
<node TEXT="&quot;Starting a Django Project The Right Way,&quot; I&apos;ll outline the steps I&apos;ve" ID="ID_1085645328" CREATED="1406792949855" MODIFIED="1406792949855"/>
<node TEXT="found to be necessary when open-sourcing a Python project." ID="ID_1885200481" CREATED="1406792949856" MODIFIED="1406792949856"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="Update (Aug 17): Thanks to @pydanny for alerting me about the" ID="ID_41470061" CREATED="1406792949856" MODIFIED="1406792949856">
<node TEXT="existence of Cookiecutter, an awesome project by @audreyr. I&apos;ve added" ID="ID_1646445150" CREATED="1406792949857" MODIFIED="1406792949857"/>
<node TEXT="a section on it to the end of this article. Be sure to check out" ID="ID_319071019" CREATED="1406792949857" MODIFIED="1406792949857"/>
<node TEXT="Audrey&apos;s awesome project!" ID="ID_346231752" CREATED="1406792949857" MODIFIED="1406792949857"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="Update 2 (Aug 18): Thanks to @ChristianHeimes (and others) for" ID="ID_655250318" CREATED="1406792949858" MODIFIED="1406792949858">
<node TEXT="suggesting a section on tox. Christian also reminded me about PEP 440" ID="ID_1450248441" CREATED="1406792949858" MODIFIED="1406792949858"/>
<node TEXT="and had some great suggestions for other minor improvements, all of" ID="ID_1849695124" CREATED="1406792949858" MODIFIED="1406792949858"/>
<node TEXT="which have been implemented." ID="ID_558549087" CREATED="1406792949859" MODIFIED="1406792949859"/>
</node>
<node TEXT="Tools and Concepts" ID="ID_1591592654" CREATED="1406792949859" MODIFIED="1406792949859">
<node TEXT="In particular, there are a number of tools and concepts I&apos;ve found" ID="ID_732170759" CREATED="1406792949860" MODIFIED="1406792949860"/>
<node TEXT="useful or necessary. I&apos;ll cover each of the topics below, including" ID="ID_382515536" CREATED="1406792949860" MODIFIED="1406792949860"/>
<node TEXT="the precise commands you&apos;ll need to run and configuration values" ID="ID_1618726301" CREATED="1406792949860" MODIFIED="1406792949860"/>
<node TEXT="you&apos;ll need to set. The goal is to make the entire process clear and" ID="ID_289530232" CREATED="1406792949860" MODIFIED="1406792949860"/>
<node TEXT="simple." ID="ID_709174037" CREATED="1406792949860" MODIFIED="1406792949860"/>
<node TEXT="Table of content" ID="ID_435936159" CREATED="1406792949860" MODIFIED="1406792949860">
